  4→ * Milestone 2: Brain auto-discovers OAuth requirements from MCP server URL
  5→ * using Protected Resource Metadata (RFC 9728) and Auth Server Metadata (RFC 8414).
  6→ * MSW simulates the external MCP server and OAuth authorization server.
  7→ *
  8→ * Traces: US-2, FR-2, AC-2a..AC-2f
  9→ * Driving port: POST /api/workspaces/:wsId/mcp-servers/:id/discover-auth
 10→ *
 11→ * Implementation sequence:
 12→ *   1. Discover auth from Protected Resource Metadata              [@skip]
 13→ *   2. Discover auth from WWW-Authenticate header on 401           [@skip]
 14→ *   3. Auth server metadata with path component (multi-fallback)   [@skip]
 15→ *   4. Discovery fails gracefully (no metadata)                    [@skip]
 16→ *   5. Auto-created credential_provider from discovery             [@skip]
